
                                                        +-------+
                                                        |  .MC  |
                                                        +-------+

MULTIPLE COLUMN  restores the  columns-per-page environment  that
was in effect  just before the last-executed  Single Column (.SC)
control word.

     +-------+---------------------------------------------+
     |       |                                             |
     |  .MC  |                                             |
     |       |                                             |
     +-------+---------------------------------------------+

This control  word causes a break.    It takes no  operands.   If
Single Column (.SC)  had not been previously specified,  no other
action is taken.

